data.description:
Come and see this charming starter Home . Enjoy 4bedrooms and 2 bath with a spacious living room , the kitchen comes with granite counter top and leads you to a converted garage through the laundry room  . The back yard is a great big Area for family BBQ's and gatherings , it also has a back gate to a alleyway.  Garage was converted to a Bedroom with closet .
House is SOLD AS IS , no repairs
Seller is very motivated
